      "domain": "www.ipayx.ai",
      "page_title": "iPayX Protocol — FINTRAC-registered FX forensic audit layer",
      "content": "iPayX Protocol — Neutral FX Verification Layer\n        iPayX Protocol is the neutral FX verification layer for fintech sales teams and FX brokers. We audit foreign-exchange transactions, compare the rate a bank or card network applied against the real-time mid-market rate, reveal invisible spreads, quantify FX costs, and project annual savings.\n        How It Works\n        \n          - Enter your transaction – Amount, currencies (e.g. CAD → USD), and the rate your bank applied.\n- We capture the mid-market rate – From regulated interbank data sources at the exact transaction time.\n- Instant audit report – Spread %, FX cost in your base currency, execution grade (A/B/C), and annual savings projection.\nTrust & Compliance\n        MSB FINTRAC C10001283 | 0-custody | AES-256 | Built in Canada 🇨🇦\n        Links\n        \n        Contact: info@ipayx.ai",
      "is_official": true,
      "retrieved_at": "2026-07-13T20:13:42.870683Z",
